Installation and running:

  Just execute the given exe, no installation is needed.


Movement and keys:

  Keys are:

    WASD for movement
    hold left shift to run
    space to jump
    look around with mouse

  You can grab objects by pointing on them and holding your left mouse button.
  While holding, you can throw the grabbed object with mouse right-click.

  Use this information to start bowling!


How to bowl:

  Grab the ball, aim at the pins, and throw it! Awesome, right! r-right?!
